00:55:34.360 --> 00:55:40.550
But even so, that
eyewear, I felt

00:55:40.550 --> 00:55:46.610
as an imposition in that
trust relationship, personal.

00:55:46.610 --> 00:55:48.060
Anyway.

00:55:48.060 --> 00:55:49.100
Anything else?

00:55:49.100 --> 00:55:50.974
Oh, one-- Yes, please.

00:55:50.974 --> 00:55:52.140
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE] legal.

