00:55:59.610 --> 00:56:01.776
AUDIENCE: How much of it
is driven by legal reasons,

00:56:01.776 --> 00:56:04.069
and not like big
data and collecting?

00:56:04.069 --> 00:56:04.860
VICTORIA SWEET: Oh.

00:56:04.860 --> 00:56:05.430
I see what you mean.

00:56:05.430 --> 00:56:07.010
AUDIENCE: By having
a paper trail and--

00:56:07.010 --> 00:56:07.270
VICTORIA SWEET: Yes.

00:56:07.270 --> 00:56:07.470
Yes.

00:56:07.470 --> 00:56:07.970
Yes.

00:56:07.970 --> 00:56:13.460
Well, we have we do like to
