00:56:16.740 --> 00:56:19.545
It doesn't have to be in
a computer per se, at all.

00:56:22.050 --> 00:56:24.570
So there's no
reason that we have

00:56:24.570 --> 00:56:26.700
to have a clumsy electronic
health record, that

00:56:26.700 --> 00:56:31.170
takes all our time and produces
big data, in order to document.

00:56:31.170 --> 00:56:33.630
It's actually much
better documentation

