This 32-year-old woman came
in with chronic headaches.

00:56:38.920 --> 00:56:40.224
And I thought this.

00:56:40.224 --> 00:56:40.890
And we did this.

00:56:40.890 --> 00:56:43.050
And this is what I think
it is, kind of the story,

00:56:43.050 --> 00:56:46.140
than it is to have what I
found with my father, which

00:56:46.140 --> 00:56:48.480
was incomprehensible.

