sorry-- this little
sublaw thingy,

00:57:08.730 --> 00:57:10.730
that every doctor,
that has anything

00:57:10.730 --> 00:57:12.480
to do with the federal
government I think,

00:57:12.480 --> 00:57:14.640
has to have their
electronic health records.

00:57:14.640 --> 00:57:15.856
That's how it happened.

00:57:15.856 --> 00:57:16.980
It didn't happen gradually.

00:57:16.980 --> 00:57:18.032
It was like 2009.

00:57:18.032 --> 00:57:20.490
And then they would start taking
money out of your practice

00:57:20.490 --> 00:57:22.560
if you didn't have
electronic records.

00:57:22.560 --> 00:57:25.080
